c: 4
v: 36
t: "waebdu allah wanqadu lah whdh, wala tajealuu lah shrykana fi alrbwbyt walebadt, wa'ahsanuu 'iilaa alwaldyn, waddu hqwqhma, wahuquq alaqrbyn, walyatamaa walmhtajyn, waljar alqarib minkum walbeyd, walrfyq fi alsafar wafi alhdr, walmsafr almhtaj, walmmalyk min ftyankm wftyatkm. 'iina allah taealaa la yuhibu almutakabirin min ebadh, almftkhryn ealaa alnas"